%% Data Flow Diagram: vllm-orchestrator-gateway
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Notebook/App)
    participant Gateway as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant LLM as vLLM Backend
    participant Detector as Detector Services<br/>(e.g., regex-detector)

    Note over Client,Detector: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8090/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: Authorization header (pass-through)
    Note over Gateway: Injects detector config<br/>based on route mapping
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8085/TCP<br/>Auth: mTLS (optional) + forwarded Authorization
    Orchestrator->>Detector: Content detection request<br/>(input filtering)
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>LLM: LLM inference request
    LLM-->>Orchestrator: Generated response
    Orchestrator->>Detector: Content detection request<br/>(output filtering)
    Detector-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: Response with detections + warnings
    Note over Gateway: If detections found &<br/>fallback_message configured:<br/>replace content with fallback
    Gateway-->>Client: OpenAI-compatible JSON response<br/>+ detections + warnings fields

    Note over Client,Detector: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion (SSE)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>stream: true<br/>HTTP 8090/TCP (plaintext)
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>SSE stream request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8085/TCP
    loop Each SSE Chunk
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: SSE chunk with delta content + detections
        Note over Gateway: Inspect chunk for detections<br/>If detected + fallback configured:<br/>modify delta, set finish_reason: "stop"
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE chunk (OpenAI-compatible)
    end
    Gateway-->>Client: SSE: [DONE]
